{"tid":1601030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部：美國就佔中五周年發表聲明，是令世人不齒的「拙劣表演」","createTime":"2019-09-29T00:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T05:44:41.000Z","uid":42188,"like":36,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e26f0c0ffe6e990d291d5cfe6fb78db64bb4b352","tid":1601030,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:43:40.000Z","msg":"外交部駐港公署發言人表示,美國國會及行政當局中國委員會,就香港「佔中」五周年發表的聲明,罔顧事實,顛倒黑白,粗暴干涉中國內政,形容是令世人不齒的「拙劣表演」,中方對此表示強烈不滿和堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n發言人指,當前香港面臨的問題,根本不是甚麼人權、民主問題,極少數暴力份子肆意打人及縱火,暴力襲擊警員及普通市民,踐踏道德底線,突破法治底線,褻瀆民主,亦是對大多數香港同胞民主權利的侵犯。<br />\n<br />\n發言人強調,美國一些議員為一己政治私利,推動涉港法案,損害包括香港同胞在內的中國人民利益,最終亦將損害美國自身利益。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#搬石頭砸自己腳<br />\n#注定失敗<br />\n#玩火自焚<br />\n#拙劣表演<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c8cffd40472b257ef64b2b191a67579eb8ff22","tid":1601030,"uid":18477,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:45:39.000Z","msg":"✅官方承認正確"},{"pid":"9f714a7b01fe09d435358c13fd6cd7ee11456e7b","tid":1601030,"uid":13592,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:51:31.000Z","msg":"屌 一篇文冇內容嘅"},{"pid":"4f8f719578ce0b425fbd329f6c694120e9b5ac88","tid":1601030,"uid":17859,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:51:33.000Z","msg":"咁拙劣都只係得強烈不滿咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da5599dac085e43137fb699a0158b2bc2aaeeb9","tid":1601030,"uid":32577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:57:13.000Z","msg":"幾時先出兵？"},{"pid":"1653dadd1b35b145c8c46f74a3abc1cd381db9d3","tid":1601030,"uid":81968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:57:18.000Z","msg":"下一篇：中方對